# Partial Least Squares (PLS) regression in C++, using Eigen.

## Quick Start

1. clone the repository, as its own project or as submodule
2. build the library: navigate to project folder, `cmake .; make pls` it
3. in whatever other code will be incorporating it, add the relevant cmake pathing to find it

